description: Associates the specified application with the specified fleet. This is only supported for Elastic fleets.

nested_items.name: ApplicationFleetAssociation
nested_items.description: If fleet name is specified, this returns the list of applications that are associated to it. If application ARN is specified, this returns the list of fleets to which it is associated.

nested_items.name: FleetName
nested_items.description: The name of the fleet associated with the application.

nested_items.name: ApplicationArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the application associated with the fleet.
